cmky0vsd7000p38zvt59zjzb5	cmjrjorwn0003b3n6srvqqp17	Which term refers to a licensee focusing on a specific neighborhood to cultivate business?	{Blockbusting,Farming,Steering,Targeting}	1	{"correct": "Farming is the practice of specializing in a particular neighborhood or property type to become the expert in that area.", "incorrect": ["Blockbusting. Blockbusting is the illegal act of inducing panic selling by suggesting minorities are moving into the area.<div><br></div>", "", "Steering is the illegal practice of guiding buyers toward or away from neighborhoods based on protected class status.", "Targeting is a general marketing term, but farming is the specific industry term for geographic specialization in real estate."]}	0	chapter	2026-01-28 12:49:49.854	2026-01-28 12:49:49.854	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1769604580615-Farming_is_the_pract.mp3	/timestamps/1769604580615-Farming_is_the_pract.timestamps.json	["/audio/1769604581882-Blockbusting__Blockb.mp3", "", "/audio/1769604583124-Steering_is_the_ille.mp3", "/audio/1769604584465-Targeting_is_a_gener.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1769604581882-Blockbusting__Blockb.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1769604583124-Steering_is_the_ille.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1769604584465-Targeting_is_a_gener.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1769604577100-Blockbusting.mp3", "/audio/1769604578044-Farming.mp3", "/audio/1769604578705-Steering.mp3", "/audio/1769604579315-Targeting.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1769604577100-Blockbusting.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1769604578044-Farming.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1769604578705-Steering.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1769604579315-Targeting.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1769604576472-Which_term_refers_to.mp3	/timestamps/1769604576472-Which_term_refers_to.timestamps.json
cmljz789q0082r4evs2lkfv0z	cmk8if4vt0000sxhb8i62wdi6	An active duty member of the U.S. Armed Forces who is NOT practicing real estate in the private sector is exempt from which of the following?	{"Continuing education only","License renewal fees only","Both license renewal fees and continuing education requirements","Initial application fees only"}	2	{"correct": "Active duty members not practicing in the private sector are exempt from all renewal requirements (fees and CE) during their service and for a period after discharge.", "incorrect": ["They are also exempt from fees.&nbsp;", "They are also exempt from CE if not practicing.", "", "This question refers to renewal status, not initial application."]}	21	chapter	2026-02-12 21:33:40.382	2026-02-12 21:33:40.382	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1770932014830-Active_duty_members_.mp3	/timestamps/1770932014830-Active_duty_members_.timestamps.json	["/audio/1770932015542-They_are_also_exempt.mp3", "/audio/1770932016437-They_are_also_exempt.mp3", "", "/audio/1770932017846-This_question_refers.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770932015542-They_are_also_exempt.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932016437-They_are_also_exempt.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1770932017846-This_question_refers.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1770932011200-Continuing_education.mp3", "/audio/1770932011787-License_renewal_fees.mp3", "/audio/1770932012814-Both_license_renewal.mp3", "/audio/1770932013441-Initial_application_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770932011200-Continuing_education.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932011787-License_renewal_fees.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932012814-Both_license_renewal.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932013441-Initial_application_.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1770932010310-An_active_duty_membe.mp3	/timestamps/1770932010310-An_active_duty_membe.timestamps.json
cmlk102zr008qr4ev1norovgj	cmk8if4vt0000sxhb8i62wdi6	Which professional is exempt from the 63-hour sales associate pre-licensing course?	{"A licensed CPA","An active member of The Florida Bar","A teacher with a master's degree","A licensed appraiser"}	1	{"correct": "Rule 61J2-3.008(8) exempts active Florida Bar members from the sales associate pre-licensing course (though not the state exam).", "incorrect": ["CPAs are not exempt from real estate education.", "", "A general master's degree does not grant exemption; only a real estate degree does.", "Appraisers are not exempt from the real estate sales associate course."]}	33	chapter	2026-02-12 22:24:06.183	2026-02-12 22:24:06.183	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1770935038785-Rule_61J2_3_008_8__e.mp3	/timestamps/1770935038785-Rule_61J2_3_008_8__e.timestamps.json	["/audio/1770935039850-CPAs_are_not_exempt_.mp3", "", "/audio/1770935040926-A_general_master_s_d.mp3", "/audio/1770935041873-Appraisers_are_not_e.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770935039850-CPAs_are_not_exempt_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1770935040926-A_general_master_s_d.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935041873-Appraisers_are_not_e.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1770935034438-A_licensed_CPA.mp3", "/audio/1770935035127-An_active_member_of_.mp3", "/audio/1770935035942-A_teacher_with_a_mas.mp3", "/audio/1770935036605-A_licensed_appraiser.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770935034438-A_licensed_CPA.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935035127-An_active_member_of_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935035942-A_teacher_with_a_mas.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935036605-A_licensed_appraiser.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1770935033899-Which_professional_i.mp3	/timestamps/1770935033899-Which_professional_i.timestamps.json
cmlk13kou008sr4evdr05n00f	cmk8if4vt0000sxhb8i62wdi6	An active member of the Florida Bar wants to become a real estate broker. Which statement is TRUE regarding their education requirements?	{"They are exempt from both the sales associate and broker pre-license courses","They must take the 72-hour broker pre-license course","They are exempt from the broker course but must take the post-license course","They are automatically granted a broker license upon application"}	1	{"correct": "Attorneys are exempt from the sales associate pre-license course (Course I) but are NOT exempt from the broker pre-license course (Course II).", "incorrect": ["They are not exempt from the broker course.&nbsp;", "", "This is reversed; they are exempt from the sales course, not the broker course.&nbsp;", "Licensure is never automatic; they must still apply and pass the state exam."]}	34	chapter	2026-02-12 22:26:49.086	2026-02-12 22:26:49.086	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1770935193981-Attorneys_are_exempt.mp3	/timestamps/1770935193981-Attorneys_are_exempt.timestamps.json	["/audio/1770935194674-They_are_not_exempt_.mp3", "", "/audio/1770935196187-This_is_reversed__th.mp3", "/audio/1770935197721-Licensure_is_never_a.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770935194674-They_are_not_exempt_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1770935196187-This_is_reversed__th.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935197721-Licensure_is_never_a.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1770935189143-They_are_exempt_from.mp3", "/audio/1770935190052-They_must_take_the_7.mp3", "/audio/1770935191070-They_are_exempt_from.mp3", "/audio/1770935192395-They_are_automatical.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770935189143-They_are_exempt_from.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935190052-They_must_take_the_7.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935191070-They_are_exempt_from.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770935192395-They_are_automatical.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1770935187800-An_active_member_of_.mp3	/timestamps/1770935187800-An_active_member_of_.timestamps.json
cmljzrdai0086r4evt8twuobb	cmk8if4vt0000sxhb8i62wdi6	What happens if an applicant has a "sealed" criminal record?	{"They never have to disclose it","It is automatically erased from all databases","They should verify if it needs to be disclosed, as many sealed records must still be reported to the DBPR","They only disclose it if asked in an interview."}	2	{"correct": "They should verify if it needs to be disclosed, as many sealed records must still be reported to the DBPR. While some expunged records are exempt, many sealed records must still be disclosed for professional licensure. It is crucial to check the specific question on the application.", "incorrect": ["This is dangerous advice, failure to disclose can lead to denial.&nbsp;", "Background checks for licensure are thorough and may still reveal sealed info.&nbsp;", "", "Disclosure happens on the written application, not just in an interview."]}	23	chapter	2026-02-12 21:49:20.01	2026-02-12 21:49:20.01	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1770932951817-They_should_verify_i.mp3	/timestamps/1770932951817-They_should_verify_i.timestamps.json	["/audio/1770932952740-This_is_dangerous_ad.mp3", "/audio/1770932953709-Background_checks_fo.mp3", "", "/audio/1770932955111-Disclosure_happens_o.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770932952740-This_is_dangerous_ad.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932953709-Background_checks_fo.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1770932955111-Disclosure_happens_o.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1770932946109-They_never_have_to_d.mp3", "/audio/1770932947534-It_is_automatically_.mp3", "/audio/1770932948800-They_should_verify_i.mp3", "/audio/1770932949575-They_only_disclose_i.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1770932946109-They_never_have_to_d.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932947534-It_is_automatically_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932948800-They_should_verify_i.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1770932949575-They_only_disclose_i.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1770932945193-What_happens_if_an_a.mp3	/timestamps/1770932945193-What_happens_if_an_a