cmloamr1c00czr4evko8xge9r	cmlo3p21500b9r4evvq0cbmdp	What condition must be met for the armed forces renewal exemption to be valid?	{" The member must not actively engage in real estate practices during the exemption period","The member must be an officer","The member must remain in Florida","The member must pay half the fees"}	0	{"correct": "The exemption is valid, assuming the service member is not actively engaging in real estate practices.", "incorrect": ["", "Rank is not the condition", "Residency location is not the condition", "The exemption covers provisions (fees/education), not just half"]}	15	chapter	2026-02-15 22:04:44.947	2026-02-19 16:50:36.009	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771519826695-The_exemption_is_val.mp3	/timestamps/1771519826695-The_exemption_is_val.timestamps.json	["", "/audio/1771519827284-Rank_is_not_the_cond.mp3", "/audio/1771519828031-Residency_location_i.mp3", "/audio/1771519829224-The_exemption_covers.mp3"]	["", "/timestamps/1771519827284-Rank_is_not_the_cond.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771519828031-Residency_location_i.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771519829224-The_exemption_covers.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771519823695-The_member_must_not_.mp3", "/audio/1771519824327-The_member_must_be_a.mp3", "/audio/1771519825021-The_member_must_rema.mp3", "/audio/1771519825671-The_member_must_pay_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771519823695-The_member_must_not_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771519824327-The_member_must_be_a.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771519825021-The_member_must_rema.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771519825671-The_member_must_pay_.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771519822426-What_condition_must_.mp3	/timestamps/1771519822426-What_condition_must_.timestamps.json
