cmlobljgu00d3r4ev5lipdh8w	cmlo3p21500b9r4evvq0cbmdp	A resident licensee who moves out of the state must notify the Commission within how many days of the change in residency?	{"10 days","30 days","60 days","90 days"}	2	{"correct": "Resident licensees moving out of state must notify the Commission within 60 days of the change in residency.", "incorrect": ["10 days is for a standard address change.", "30 days is incorrect.", "", "90 days is incorrect."]}	17	chapter	2026-02-15 22:31:48.112	2026-02-16 13:58:23.676	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771250301093-Resident_licensees_m.mp3	/timestamps/1771250301093-Resident_licensees_m.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771250302168-10_days_is_for_a_sta.mp3", "/audio/1771250302782-30_days_is_incorrect.mp3", "", "/audio/1771250303445-90_days_is_incorrect.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250302168-10_days_is_for_a_sta.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250302782-30_days_is_incorrect.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771250303445-90_days_is_incorrect.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771250298091-10_days.mp3", "/audio/1771250298655-30_days.mp3", "/audio/1771250299257-60_days.mp3", "/audio/1771250299807-90_days.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250298091-10_days.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250298655-30_days.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250299257-60_days.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250299807-90_days.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771250297560-A_resident_licensee_.mp3	/timestamps/1771250297560-A_resident_licensee_.timestamps.json
cmlocfewi00d5r4eva6ye3gom	cmlo3p21500b9r4evvq0cbmdp	What is a "Group License"?	{"A license for a broker who holds more than one broker's license","A license for an associate employed by an owner-developer to work on separate sales projects","A license for a team of agents sharing commissions","A license for a corporation"}	1	{"correct": "A group license as one issued to an associate employed by an owner- who owns properties in the name of various entities.", "incorrect": ["This describes Multiple Licenses.", "", "Team sharing is not the definition of a group license.", "A corporation license is different from a group license for an individual associate."]}	18	chapter	2026-02-15 22:55:01.87	2026-02-16 13:58:31.848	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771250309225-A_group_license_as_o.mp3	/timestamps/1771250309225-A_group_license_as_o.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771250310003-This_describes_Multi.mp3", "", "/audio/1771250310699-Team_sharing_is_not_.mp3", "/audio/1771250311688-A_corporation_licens.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250310003-This_describes_Multi.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771250310699-Team_sharing_is_not_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250311688-A_corporation_licens.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771250305323-A_license_for_a_brok.mp3", "/audio/1771250306369-A_license_for_an_ass.mp3", "/audio/1771250307140-A_license_for_a_team.mp3", "/audio/1771250307939-A_license_for_a_corp.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250305323-A_license_for_a_brok.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250306369-A_license_for_an_ass.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250307140-A_license_for_a_team.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250307939-A_license_for_a_corp.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771250304441-What_is_a__Group_Lic.mp3	/timestamps/1771250304441-What_is_a__Group_Lic.timestamps.json
cmloco6sh00d7r4evttis06y4	cmlo3p21500b9r4evvq0cbmdp	For their service, the members of FREC receive:&nbsp;	{"An annual salary ","Per day when they are needed ","$50 per day when on official business, plus out-of-pocket travel expenses","Zero compensation "}	2	{"correct": "Florida Statute 475.02 states that Commission members shall receive $50 per day for each day they attend an official meeting or participate in official Commission business. They are also reimbursed for expenses (like mileage and hotels) incurred in the performance of their duties.<div><br></div>", "incorrect": ["Commission members are volunteers and do not receive an annual salary.", "This answer is too vague; the law specifically sets the rate at $50 per day, not an undefined \\"per day\\" rate.", "", "While they are volunteers, they are not expected to pay their own way. They receive the $50 per diem and expense reimbursement, so \\"zero\\" is incorrect."]}	19	chapter	2026-02-15 23:01:51.291	2026-02-16 13:58:42.678	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771250318509-Florida_Statute_475_.mp3	/timestamps/1771250318509-Florida_Statute_475_.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771250319693-Commission_members_a.mp3", "/audio/1771250321021-This_answer_is_too_v.mp3", "", "/audio/1771250322520-While_they_are_volun.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250319693-Commission_members_a.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250321021-This_answer_is_too_v.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771250322520-While_they_are_volun.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771250313241-An_annual_salary.mp3", "/audio/1771250313996-Per_day_when_they_ar.mp3", "/audio/1771250315020-_50_per_day_when_on_.mp3", "/audio/1771250315635-Zero_compensation.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771250313241-An_annual_salary.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250313996-Per_day_when_they_ar.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250315020-_50_per_day_when_on_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771250315635-Zero_compensation.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771250312695-For_their_service__t.mp3	/timestamps/1771250312695-For_t