cmmqezvkl002m4be7nygaffz6	cmmqbpz7v00044be7x0za79d7	&nbsp;Which U.S. Supreme Court case upheld the Civil Rights Act of 1866, confirming that it applies to private real estate transactions?	{"Brown v. Board of Education","Jones v. Mayer","Roe v. Wade","Miranda v. Arizona"}	1	{"correct": "Jones v. Mayer (1968) confirmed that the 1866 Act prohibits all racial discrimination in real estate, whether by the government or private citizens.", "incorrect": ["Ended segregation in public schools.", "", "Dealt with abortion rights.", "Established rights for criminal suspects."]}	3	chapter	2026-03-14 14:22:10.581	2026-03-14 23:11:42.014	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1773529898929-Jones_v__Mayer__1968.mp3	/timestamps/1773529898929-Jones_v__Mayer__1968.timestamps.json	["/audio/1773529899940-Ended_segregation_in.mp3", "", "/audio/1773529900765-Dealt_with_abortion_.mp3", "/audio/1773529901779-Established_rights_f.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773529899940-Ended_segregation_in.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1773529900765-Dealt_with_abortion_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529901779-Established_rights_f.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1773529894526-Brown_v__Board_of_Ed.mp3", "/audio/1773529895337-Jones_v__Mayer.mp3", "/audio/1773529896011-Roe_v__Wade.mp3", "/audio/1773529896820-Miranda_v__Arizona.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773529894526-Brown_v__Board_of_Ed.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529895337-Jones_v__Mayer.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529896011-Roe_v__Wade.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529896820-Miranda_v__Arizona.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1773529893773-Which_U_S__Supreme_C.mp3	/timestamps/1773529893773-Which_U_S__Supreme_C.timestamps.json
cmlppkuyy00iwr4evikiblamh	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	A Transaction Broker provides which type of representation?	{"Fiduciary representation to one party","Limited representation to a buyer, a seller, or both","Full representation to both parties","No representation to either party"}	1	{"correct": "A transaction broker provides \\"limited representation\\" to a buyer, seller, or both, without acting as a fiduciary.", "incorrect": ["Fiduciary representation is characteristic of a Single Agent, not a Transaction Broker.", "", "Full\\" representation implies fiduciary duties, which a Transaction Broker does not provide.", "\\"No representation\\" refers to the No Brokerage Relationship status."]}	3	chapter	2026-02-16 21:50:57.226	2026-02-16 23:15:24.111	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283720987-A_transaction_broker.mp3	/timestamps/1771283720987-A_transaction_broker.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283722065-Fiduciary_representa.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283723081-Full__representation.mp3", "/audio/1771283723952-_No_representation__.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283722065-Fiduciary_representa.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283723081-Full__representation.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283723952-_No_representation__.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283717156-Fiduciary_representa.mp3", "/audio/1771283717989-Limited_representati.mp3", "/audio/1771283718835-Full_representation_.mp3", "/audio/1771283719485-No_representation_to.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283717156-Fiduciary_representa.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283717989-Limited_representati.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283718835-Full_representation_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283719485-No_representation_to.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283716401-A_Transaction_Broker.mp3	/timestamps/1771283716401-A_Transaction_Broker.timestamps.json
cmlpq35em00j0r4evwdppcjg3	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	To transition from a Single Agent to a Transaction Broker, what must the principal do?	{"Verbally agree to the change","Sign or initial the Consent to Transition to Transaction Broker disclosure","Pay an additional fee","Terminate the original listing agreement"}	1	{"correct": "The change can only occur with express written permission, specifically by signing or initialing the Consent to Transition disclosure.", "incorrect": ["Verbal agreement is insufficient; express written permission is required.", "", "The text mentions no fee requirement for this transition.", "The relationship is modified via the disclosure, not by terminating the agreement entirely."]}	5	chapter	2026-02-16 22:05:10.557	2026-02-16 23:15:44.445	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283741170-The_change_can_only_.mp3	/timestamps/1771283741170-The_change_can_only_.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283742283-Verbal_agreement_is_.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283743127-The_text_mentions_no.mp3", "/audio/1771283744199-The_relationship_is_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283742283-Verbal_agreement_is_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283743127-The_text_mentions_no.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283744199-The_relationship_is_.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283737324-Verbally_agree_to_th.mp3", "/audio/1771283738325-Sign_or_initial_the_.mp3", "/audio/1771283739032-Pay_an_additional_fe.mp3", "/audio/1771283739706-Terminate_the_origin.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283737324-Verbally_agree_to_th.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283738325-Sign_or_initial_the_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283739032-Pay_an_additional_fe.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283739706-Terminate_the_origin.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283736591-To_transition_from_a.mp3	/timestamps/1771283736591-To_transition_from_a.timestamps.json
cmlpq4sdk00j2r4evop2td51j	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	For how long must brokers retain brokerage relationship disclosure documents?<div><br></div>	{"Two years","Five years","Ten years",Forever}	1	{"correct": "Brokers must retain disclosure documents for five years for all relevant transactions.", "incorrect": ["Two years is incorrect. The requirement is five years.", "", "Ten years is incorrect. The requirement is five years.", "Indefinite retention is not required. The requirement is five years."]}	6	chapter	2026-02-16 22:06:26.983	2026-02-16 23:15:51.699	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283748759-Brokers_must_retain_.mp3	/timestamps/1771283748759-Brokers_must_retain_.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283749779-Two_years_is_incorre.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283750728-Ten_years_is_incorre.mp3", "/audio/1771283751540-Indefinite_retention.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283749779-Two_years_is_incorre.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283750728-Ten_years_is_incorre.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283751540-Indefinite_retention.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283746007-Two_years.mp3", "/audio/1771283746481-Five_years.mp3", "/audio/1771283747081-Ten_years.mp3", "/audio/1771283747655-Forever.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283746007-Two_years.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283746481-Five_years.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283747081-Ten_years.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283747655-Forever.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283745537-For_how_long_must_br.mp3	/timestamps/1771283745537-For_how_long_must_br.timestamps.json
cmlpqahgp00j6r4ev73umqigg	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	In a Designated Sales Associate arrangement, what is the role of the Broker?	{"To act as a Single Agent for both parties","To act as a neutral party advising the designated sales associates","To represent only the seller","To have no involvement in the transaction"}	1	{"correct": "The broker acts as a \\"neutral party advising the designated sales associates to help facilitate the process.”", "incorrect": ["The broker cannot be a Single Agent for both (Dual Agency); only the associates take on fiduciary roles.", "", "The broker remains neutral, not siding with the seller.", "The broker is involved as an advisor and facilitator, not completely uninvolved."]}	8	chapter	2026-02-16 22:10:52.777	2026-02-16 23:16:13.541	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283770218-The_broker_acts_as_a.mp3	/timestamps/1771283770218-The_broker_acts_as_a.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283771504-The_broker_cannot_be.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283772353-The_broker_remains_n.mp3", "/audio/1771283773346-The_broker_is_involv.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283771504-The_broker_cannot_be.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283772353-The_broker_remains_n.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283773346-The_broker_is_involv.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283766548-To_act_as_a_Single_A.mp3", "/audio/1771283767410-To_act_as_a_neutral_.mp3", "/audio/1771283768043-To_represent_only_th.mp3", "/audio/1771283768881-To_have_no_involveme.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283766548-To_act_as_a_Single_A.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283767410-To_act_as_a_neutral_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283768043-To_represent_only_th.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283768881-To_have_no_involveme.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283765849-In_a_Designated_Sale.mp3	/timestamps/1771283765849-In_a_Designated_Sale.timestamps.json
cmlpqc9qd00j8r4evq3y16e0f	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	What is the minimum asset requirement for a buyer and seller to use Designated Sales Associates?	{"$500,000 each","$1 million each","$1 million combined","$2 million each"}	1	{"correct": "The buyer and the seller must each have assets of $1 million or more.", "incorrect": ["This amount is lower than the mandatory threshold of $1 million.&nbsp;", "", "The requirement is $1 million each, not combined.", "While $2 million qualifies, the minimum requirement is $1 million."]}	9	chapter	2026-02-16 22:12:16.069	2026-02-16 23:16:21.944	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283778649-The_buyer_and_the_se.mp3	/timestamps/1771283778649-The_buyer_and_the_se.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283779672-This_amount_is_lower.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283780644-The_requirement_is__.mp3", "/audio/1771283781727-While__2_million_qua.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283779672-This_amount_is_lower.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283780644-The_requirement_is__.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283781727-While__2_million_qua.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283775547-_500_000_each.mp3", "/audio/1771283776248-_1_million_each.mp3", "/audio/1771283776905-_1_million_combined.mp3", "/audio/1771283777555-_2_million_each.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283775547-_500_000_each.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283776248-_1_million_each.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283776905-_1_million_combined.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283777555-_2_million_each.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283774832-What_is_the_minimum_.mp3	/timestamps/1771283774832-What_is_the_minimum_.timestamps.json
cmmqf2sh1002o4be79ee2wyi7	cmmqbpz7v00044be7x0za79d7	The Civil Rights Act of 1968, also known as the Fair Housing Act, prohibits discrimination in which specific activity?	{"Employment hiring","Public school admissions","The sale, rental, and financing of housing","Voting rights"}	2	{"correct": "Title VIII of the 1968 Act (Fair Housing Act) specifically governs the sale, rental, financing, and advertising of housing.", "incorrect": ["Covered by the Civil Rights Act of 1964.", "Addressed by Brown v. Board and the 1964 Act.", "", "Covered by the Voting Rights Act of 1965."]}	4	chapter	2026-03-14 14:24:26.532	2026-03-14 23:11:51.19	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1773529908239-Title_VIII_of_the_19.mp3	/timestamps/1773529908239-Title_VIII_of_the_19.timestamps.json	["/audio/1773529909123-Covered_by_the_Civil.mp3", "/audio/1773529910002-Addressed_by_Brown_v.mp3", "", "/audio/1773529911038-Covered_by_the_Votin.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773529909123-Covered_by_the_Civil.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529910002-Addressed_by_Brown_v.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1773529911038-Covered_by_the_Votin.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1773529904450-Employment_hiring.mp3", "/audio/1773529905114-Public_school_admiss.mp3", "/audio/1773529905909-The_sale__rental__an.mp3", "/audio/1773529906408-Voting_rights.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773529904450-Employment_hiring.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529905114-Public_school_admiss.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529905909-The_sale__rental__an.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529906408-Voting_rights.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1773529903428-The_Civil_Rights_Act.mp3	/timestamps/1773529903428-The_Civil_Rights_Act.timestamps.json
cmlpqekwf00jar4evpq9s33s4	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	Designated Sales Associates may ONLY be used in which type of transaction?	{"Residential transactions","Nonresidential transactions","Agricultural transactions under 10 acres","Any transaction with written consent"}	1	{"correct": "This arrangement is for \\"a nonresidential transaction.”", "incorrect": ["It is not permitted in residential transactions.", "", "Agricultural land under 10 acres is defined as residential, so this would not be allowed.", "Consent is needed, but the transaction must also be nonresidential."]}	10	chapter	2026-02-16 22:14:03.855	2026-02-16 23:16:29.605	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283786574-This_arrangement_is_.mp3	/timestamps/1771283786574-This_arrangement_is_.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283787434-It_is_not_permitted_.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283788551-Agricultural_land_un.mp3", "/audio/1771283789387-Consent_is_needed__b.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283787434-It_is_not_permitted_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283788551-Agricultural_land_un.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283789387-Consent_is_needed__b.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283783552-Residential_transact.mp3", "/audio/1771283784194-Nonresidential_trans.mp3", "/audio/1771283784917-Agricultural_transac.mp3", "/audio/1771283785580-Any_transaction_with.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283783552-Residential_transact.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283784194-Nonresidential_trans.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283784917-Agricultural_transac.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283785580-Any_transaction_with.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283783015-Designated_Sales_Ass.mp3	/timestamps/1771283783015-Designated_Sales_Ass.timestamps.json
cmlpqygo800jer4evsu9rpwjd	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	Which duty is NOT required of a Transaction Broker?	{"Use skill, care, and diligence","Exercise limited confidentiality",Obedience,"Present all offers and counteroffers"}	2	{"correct": "Obedience is a fiduciary duty exclusive to Single Agents. Transaction Brokers do not owe obedience.", "incorrect": ["Using skill, care, and diligence is a required duty for Transaction Brokers.", "Exercising limited confidentiality is a required duty for Transaction Brokers.", "", "Presenting all offers is a required duty for Transaction Brokers."]}	12	chapter	2026-02-16 22:29:31.433	2026-02-16 23:16:49.262	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283806237-Obedience_is_a_fiduc.mp3	/timestamps/1771283806237-Obedience_is_a_fiduc.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283807217-Using_skill__care__a.mp3", "/audio/1771283808209-Exercising_limited_c.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283809052-Presenting_all_offer.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283807217-Using_skill__care__a.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283808209-Exercising_limited_c.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283809052-Presenting_all_offer.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283802871-Use_skill__care__and.mp3", "/audio/1771283803535-Exercise_limited_con.mp3", "/audio/1771283804035-Obedience.mp3", "/audio/1771283804876-Present_all_offers_a.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283802871-Use_skill__care__and.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283803535-Exercise_limited_con.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283804035-Obedience.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283804876-Present_all_offers_a.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283802191-Which_duty_is_NOT_re.mp3	/timestamps/1771283802191-Which_duty_is_NOT_re.timestamps.json
cmlpqh2kg00jcr4ev5qnxtbm2	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	A broker has listed a home for sale. The seller informs the broker that one of electrical outlets is not working. To strictly fulfill their legal and ethical obligations to a prospective buyer, what must the broker tell the seller?&nbsp;	{"State that all electrical outlets appear to be in perfect working order","Inform the buyer that one specific outlet is not working","Tell the buyer they should hire a home inspector if they are worried about the electrical system","Remain silent about the issue unless the buyer specifically asks about that outlet"}	1	{"correct": "Real estate licensees have a mandatory duty to deal honestly and fairly and to disclose all known facts that materially affect the value of the property (especially those not readily observable). Since the broker knows about the defect, the only way to satisfy the legal requirement of honesty is to disclose it.", "incorrect": ["This constitutes misrepresentation (fraud). The broker knows the outlet is broken; stating it is \\"good\\" is a lie.", "", "While buyers should get inspections, a broker cannot use the suggestion of an inspection to hide a defect they already know about. You’re not allowed to hide facts you already possess.", "This could be considered concealment. If a defect is known, staying silent in hopes the buyer doesn't find it violates the duty of honesty and fairness."]}	11	chapter	2026-02-16 22:16:00.063	2026-02-16 23:16:41.296	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283797203-Real_estate_licensee.mp3	/timestamps/1771283797203-Real_estate_licensee.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283798458-This_constitutes_mis.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283799818-While_buyers_should_.mp3", "/audio/1771283801104-This_could_be_consid.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283798458-This_constitutes_mis.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283799818-While_buyers_should_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283801104-This_could_be_consid.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283792264-State_that_all_elec