cmlprckve00jgr4ev4exwnolm	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	14. When must the "No Brokerage Relationship" disclosure be provided?	{"At the closing table","Before the showing of property","Within 24 hours of meeting the client","After the first offer is written"}	1	{"correct": "No brokerage relationship disclosure must be made before the showing of property.", "incorrect": ["This is too late to satisfy the legal requirement.", "", "The requirement is linked to the showing of property, not a specific hour count.", "It must be provided before showing, which happens before offers are written."]}	13	chapter	2026-02-16 22:40:30.049	2026-02-16 23:16:57.397	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283814090-No_brokerage_relatio.mp3	/timestamps/1771283814090-No_brokerage_relatio.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283815155-This_is_too_late_to_.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283816099-The_requirement_is_l.mp3", "/audio/1771283817200-It_must_be_provided_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283815155-This_is_too_late_to_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283816099-The_requirement_is_l.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283817200-It_must_be_provided_.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283810930-At_the_closing_table.mp3", "/audio/1771283811625-Before_the_showing_o.mp3", "/audio/1771283812437-Within_24_hours_of_m.mp3", "/audio/1771283813073-After_the_first_offe.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283810930-At_the_closing_table.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283811625-Before_the_showing_o.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283812437-Within_24_hours_of_m.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283813073-After_the_first_offe.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283810223-When_must_the__No_Br.mp3	/timestamps/1771283810223-When_must_the__No_Br.timestamps.json
cmmqf5061002q4be7tudfn2vw	cmmqbpz7v00044be7x0za79d7	Which of the following is a valid exemption under the Fair Housing Act of 1968?	{"A private club providing lodging to its members (non-commercially)","A broker selling a home for a friend","A landlord refusing to rent to a generic \\"protected class\\" because of race","An apartment complex with 10 units"}	0	{"correct": "Private clubs that provide lodging to members for non-commercial purposes are exempt from the Act.", "incorrect": ["", "If a broker is used, NO exemptions apply.", "Racial discrimination is never exempt (due to the 1866 Act).", "Multifamily buildings with 5 or more units are always covered."]}	5	chapter	2026-03-14 14:26:09.816	2026-03-14 23:12:00.861	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1773529917645-Private_clubs_that_p.mp3	/timestamps/1773529917645-Private_clubs_that_p.timestamps.json	["", "/audio/1773529918504-If_a_broker_is_used_.mp3", "/audio/1773529919652-Racial_discriminatio.mp3", "/audio/1773529920633-Multifamily_building.mp3"]	["", "/timestamps/1773529918504-If_a_broker_is_used_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529919652-Racial_discriminatio.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529920633-Multifamily_building.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1773529913784-A_private_club_provi.mp3", "/audio/1773529914541-A_broker_selling_a_h.mp3", "/audio/1773529915483-A_landlord_refusing_.mp3", "/audio/1773529916285-An_apartment_complex.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773529913784-A_private_club_provi.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529914541-A_broker_selling_a_h.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529915483-A_landlord_refusing_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773529916285-An_apartment_complex.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1773529912629-Which_of_the_followi.mp3	/timestamps/1773529912629-Which_of_the_followi.timestamps.json
cmlprfp3700jir4evqquo3euw	cmlpniy5e00gyr4ev7l7y4vur	Which of the following is defined as a dual agent?	{"A broker representing both buyer and seller as a Transaction Broker","A broker representing both buyer and seller as a fiduciary in the same transaction","A broker representing a buyer as a Single Agent and a seller as a No Brokerage relationship","A sales associate working with a designated sales associate"}	1	{"correct": "A dual agent is a broker who represents both the buyer and the seller as a fiduciary in the same transaction, which is impossible.&nbsp;", "incorrect": ["Representation as a Transaction Broker is legal and is not dual agency because there is no fiduciary duty.", "", "This is a legal arrangement (Single Agent for one, no representation for the other) and is not dual agency.", "Designated sales associates are a specific legal exception, not dual agents."]}	14	chapter	2026-02-16 22:42:55.554	2026-02-16 23:17:07.753	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771283823654-A_dual_agent_is_a_br.mp3	/timestamps/1771283823654-A_dual_agent_is_a_br.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771283824970-Representation_as_a_.mp3", "", "/audio/1771283826336-This_is_a_legal_arra.mp3", "/audio/1771283827575-Designated_sales_ass.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283824970-Representation_as_a_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771283826336-This_is_a_legal_arra.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283827575-Designated_sales_ass.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771283819121-A_broker_representin.mp3", "/audio/1771283820261-A_broker_representin.mp3", "/audio/1771283821316-A_broker_representin.mp3", "/audio/1771283822130-A_sales_associate_wo.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771283819121-A_broker_representin.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283820261-A_broker_representin.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283821316-A_broker_representin.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771283822130-A_sales_associate_wo.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771283818199-Which_of_the_followi.mp3	/timestamps/1771283818199-Which_of_the_followi.timestamps.json
