cmltrh2m200p3r4evoifbmcyu	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	An advertisement that fails to include the licensed name of the brokerage firm is known as:	{"A pocket listing","A blind advertisement","A team advertisement","An institutional ad"}	1	{"correct": "A \\"blind ad\\" provides only contact info (like a phone number) without identifying the brokerage, which is illegal.", "incorrect": ["A pocket listing is a property not on the MLS.", "", "Team advertising is legal if it follows specific naming rules.", "Institutional advertising promotes the firm generally, not a specific house."]}	5	chapter	2026-02-19 17:55:04.441	2026-02-19 19:56:43.12	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531000056-A__blind_ad__provide.mp3	/timestamps/1771531000056-A__blind_ad__provide.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531001114-A_pocket_listing_is_.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531001933-Team_advertising_is_.mp3", "/audio/1771531002871-Institutional_advert.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531001114-A_pocket_listing_is_.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531001933-Team_advertising_is_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531002871-Institutional_advert.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771530997030-A_pocket_listing.mp3", "/audio/1771530997690-A_blind_advertisemen.mp3", "/audio/1771530998272-A_team_advertisement.mp3", "/audio/1771530998869-An_institutional_ad.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771530997030-A_pocket_listing.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771530997690-A_blind_advertisemen.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771530998272-A_team_advertisement.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771530998869-An_institutional_ad.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771530996413-An_advertisement_tha.mp3	/timestamps/1771530996413-An_advertisement_tha.timestamps.json
cmltrjwmt00p5r4evm0e3bq20	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	Which statement is TRUE regarding a sales associate advertising real estate services?	{"They may advertise in their own name as long as they are a top producer","They are interpreted as acting as a broker","They must include the name of the brokerage firm in the advertisement","They are not allowed to advertise on social media"}	2	{"correct": "All advertising by a sales associate must include the name of the brokerage firm they work for.", "incorrect": ["Being a top producer grants no exemption from the law.", "This is the definition of unlicensed activity; a licensed associate is acting for the broker.", "", "Social media advertising is allowed but must follow the same rules (brokerage name must be present)."]}	6	chapter	2026-02-19 17:57:16.66	2026-02-19 19:56:53.243	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531009237-All_advertising_by_a.mp3	/timestamps/1771531009237-All_advertising_by_a.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531010337-Being_a_top_producer.mp3", "/audio/1771531011878-This_is_the_definiti.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531013050-Social_media_adverti.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531010337-Being_a_top_producer.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531011878-This_is_the_definiti.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531013050-Social_media_adverti.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771531005214-They_may_advertise_i.mp3", "/audio/1771531005955-They_are_interpreted.mp3", "/audio/1771531006842-They_must_include_th.mp3", "/audio/1771531007694-They_are_not_allowed.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531005214-They_may_advertise_i.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531005955-They_are_interpreted.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531006842-They_must_include_th.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531007694-They_are_not_allowed.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771531004225-Which_statement_is_T.mp3	/timestamps/1771531004225-Which_statement_is_T.timestamps.json
cmltrmuvh00p7r4evysh8mik6	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	A sales associate owns a rental property and wants to sell it "For Sale By Owner." Which applies?	{"They are strictly prohibited from selling their own property","They must list it with their employing broker","They may sell it on their own but must disclose to the buyer that they hold a real estate license before serious negotiations","They can hide their license status to get a better price"}	2	{"correct": "Licensees can sell their own property, but they must disclose their licensee status prior to serious negotiations.", "incorrect": ["Licensees are not prohibited from selling their own assets.", "They are not required to list with their broker (unless their independent contractor agreement says so, but law permits FSBO).", "", "Hiding license status is deceptive and a violation of ethics and law."]}	7	chapter	2026-02-19 17:59:34.349	2026-02-19 19:57:04.853	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531020811-Licensees_can_sell_t.mp3	/timestamps/1771531020811-Licensees_can_sell_t.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531022217-Licensees_are_not_pr.mp3", "/audio/1771531023542-They_are_not_require.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531024565-Hiding_license_statu.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531022217-Licensees_are_not_pr.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531023542-They_are_not_require.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531024565-Hiding_license_statu.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771531015442-They_are_strictly_pr.mp3", "/audio/1771531017067-They_must_list_it_wi.mp3", "/audio/1771531018575-They_may_sell_it_on_.mp3", "/audio/1771531019385-They_can_hide_their_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531015442-They_are_strictly_pr.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531017067-They_must_list_it_wi.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531018575-They_may_sell_it_on_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531019385-They_can_hide_their_.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771531014638-A_sales_associate_ow.mp3	/timestamps/1771531014638-A_sales_associate_ow.timestamps.json
cmltrp8r500p9r4evkb37q5vd	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	Which word is PROHIBITED from being used in a real estate team name?	{Group,Team,Associates,Squad}	2	{"correct": "Words like \\"Associates,\\" \\"Realty,\\" or \\"Company\\" are prohibited because they imply the team is a separate brokerage.", "incorrect": ["\\"Group\\" is a permissible team term.", "\\"Team\\" is a permissible team term.", "", "\\"Squad\\" is generally permissible as it doesn't imply a brokerage entity."]}	8	chapter	2026-02-19 18:01:25.648	2026-02-19 19:57:12.94	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531030013-Words_like__Associat.mp3	/timestamps/1771531030013-Words_like__Associat.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531031054-_Group__is_a_permiss.mp3", "/audio/1771531031755-_Team__is_a_permissi.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531032775-_Squad__is_generally.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531031054-_Group__is_a_permiss.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531031755-_Team__is_a_permissi.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531032775-_Squad__is_generally.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771531026610-Group.mp3", "/audio/1771531027222-Team.mp3", "/audio/1771531027770-Associates.mp3", "/audio/1771531028466-Squad.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531026610-Group.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531027222-Team.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531027770-Associates.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531028466-Squad.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771531025972-Which_word_is_PROHIB.mp3	/timestamps/1771531025972-Which_word_is_PROHIB.timestamps.json
cmltrsm1000pbr4evdcund1sn	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	On a real estate website, where must the brokerage firm's name appear?	{"Only on the \\"About Us\\" page","Adjacent to or immediately above/below the point of contact information","In the website footer in 2-point font","It is not required on websites, only in print"}	1	{"correct": "The brokerage name must be near the contact info (phone/email) so the consumer knows who they are contacting.", "incorrect": ["It must appear on every page/instance where contact info is shown.", "", "It must be legible and conspicuous.", "Internet advertising is fully regulated by Chapter 475.&nbsp;"]}	9	chapter	2026-02-19 18:04:02.82	2026-02-19 19:57:22.09	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531038967-The_brokerage_name_m.mp3	/timestamps/1771531038967-The_brokerage_name_m.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531040143-It_must_appear_on_ev.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531040943-It_must_be_legible_a.mp3", "/audio/1771531041913-Internet_advertising.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531040143-It_must_appear_on_ev.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531040943-It_must_be_legible_a.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531041913-Internet_advertising.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771531034837-Only_on_the__About_U.mp3", "/audio/1771531035795-Adjacent_to_or_immed.mp3", "/audio/1771531036560-In_the_website_foote.mp3", "/audio/1771531037494-It_is_not_required_o.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531034837-Only_on_the__About_U.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531035795-Adjacent_to_or_immed.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531036560-In_the_website_foote.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531037494-It_is_not_required_o.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1771531034035-On_a_real_estate_web.mp3	/timestamps/1771531034035-On_a_real_estate_web.timestamps.json
cmlts3ta300pdr4evxsm1ciw3	cmlslqsgt00l1r4evfhnwe7be	A sales associate closed a transaction with a client 14 months ago. The client is currently listed on the National Do Not Call Registry. The associate wants to call the client to ask for a referral. Is this legally permissible?	{"No, because the client is listed on the Do Not Call Registry","Yes, because an established business relationship allows the associate to call for up to 18 months after the transaction","No, because the established business relationship exemption expires after 12 months","Yes, but only if the client signs a new waiver before the call is made"}	1	{"correct": "Federal and state laws provide an exemption for \\"Established Business Relationships.\\" A licensee may contact a past client for up to 18 months after the conclusion of a transaction, even if that client is on the registry.", "incorrect": ["The registry applies to cold calls; the existing relationship exemption overrides the registry status in this specific case.", "", "The exemption lasts for 18 months, not 12 months.", "A new waiver is not required; the previous transaction establishes the legal right to call for the 18-month period."]}	10	chapter	2026-02-19 18:12:45.344	2026-02-19 19:57:33.742	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1771531050030-Federal_and_state_la.mp3	/timestamps/1771531050030-Federal_and_state_la.timestamps.json	["/audio/1771531051460-The_registry_applies.mp3", "", "/audio/1771531052355-The_exemption_lasts_.mp3", "/audio/1771531053575-A_new_waiver_is_not_.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531051460-The_registry_applies.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1771531052355-The_exemption_lasts_.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1771531053575-A_new_waiver_is_not_.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1771531044806-No__because_the_clie.mp3", "/audio/1771531046072-Yes__because_an_esta.mp3", "/audio/1771531047303-No__because_the_esta.mp3", "/audio/1771531048167-Yes__but_only_if_the.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1771531044806-No__because_the_clie.timestamps.json", "/timestamps