cmmqm63q3003o4be7gu7wa5gr	cmmqbpz7v00044be7x0za79d7	Which phrase best describes the "15 vs. 30 Day Rule" for security deposits?	{"15 days to evict, 30 days to pay rent.","15 days to return the deposit if no claim; 30 days to notify tenant of a claim.","15 days to inspect, 30 days to repair.","15 days to hold funds, 30 days to spend them."}	1	{"correct": "This rule dictates the landlord's deadlines: 15 days to simply return the money, or 30 days to send a certified letter claiming damages.", "incorrect": ["This does not reflect the statutory deadlines for deposits.", "", "This does not reflect the statutory deadlines for deposits.", "This does not reflect the statutory deadlines for deposits."]}	22	chapter	2026-03-14 17:42:58.337	2026-03-14 23:14:43.771	\N	\N	\N	\N	/audio/1773530080654-This_rule_dictates_t.mp3	/timestamps/1773530080654-This_rule_dictates_t.timestamps.json	["/audio/1773530081865-This_does_not_reflec.mp3", "", "/audio/1773530082787-This_does_not_reflec.mp3", "/audio/1773530083589-This_does_not_reflec.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773530081865-This_does_not_reflec.timestamps.json", "", "/timestamps/1773530082787-This_does_not_reflec.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773530083589-This_does_not_reflec.timestamps.json"]	["/audio/1773530075734-15_days_to_evict__30.mp3", "/audio/1773530076925-15_days_to_return_th.mp3", "/audio/1773530077876-15_days_to_inspect__.mp3", "/audio/1773530078867-15_days_to_hold_fund.mp3"]	["/timestamps/1773530075734-15_days_to_evict__30.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773530076925-15_days_to_return_th.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773530077876-15_days_to_inspect__.timestamps.json", "/timestamps/1773530078867-15_days_to_hold_fund.timestamps.json"]	/audio/1773530074695-Which_phrase_best_de.mp3	/timestamps/1773530074695-Which_phrase_best_de.timestamps.json
